<!--**********************************************************************
    *                                                                    *
    *                        S1000D Issue 2                              *
    *                SGML Document Type Definition                       *
    *                                                                    *
    *                     Release Version 2.2                            *
    *                       Date: 2005-05-01                             *
    *                                                                    *
    * Amendment:-                                                        *
    * 1. CPF 2004-32US: Entity %APPLIC; created.                         *
    *                                                                    *
    * Typical invocation:-                                               *
    * <!ENTITY % APPLSTATIC PUBLIC                                       *
    *   "-//S1000D//ELEMENTS Applic Static Breakdown 20050501//EN" >     *
    * %APPLSTATIC;                                                       *
    ********************************************************************** -->

<!--**********************************************************************
    * Define Entity %APPLIC; (Applicability) containing:-                *
    *  type       - Optional Single      contains Parsed Character Data. *
    *  model      - Optional Repeatable  contains version, csnref, nsn,  *
    *                                             mfc, pnr, serialno,    *
    *                                             batchno, moduleno,     *
    *                                             customer, softprog,    *
    *                                             maintlevel, config.    *
    ********************************************************************** -->
<!ENTITY % APPLIC "type?,model*">
